{"id":588133,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/【朋友圈】退出中国共产党声明/","date":"2018-07-03T12:11:31Z","modified":"2018-07-03T12:11:31Z","title":"【朋友圈】退出中国共产党声明","content":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-588134\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0071-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0071-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0071-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0071-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0071.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>刚接到湖南律协党支部的电话，他们要对我做违纪处理，并要我配合他们，为了不让有关领导操心，也为了简化相关手续，互相面见不爽，我在此声明：</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>从今天起我自愿退出中国共产党，声明发出之日即是我退党之日！</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>声明人：文东海</p>\n<p>2018年7月3日</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：中国数字空间｜</strong><strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E9%80%80%E5%85%9A\">退党</a></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>03.08<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/03/%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e4%ba%9a%e6%b4%b2%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%80%e5%90%8d%e5%a5%b3%e5%85%9a%e5%91%98%e4%b8%a4%e4%bc%9a%e6%9c%9f%e9%97%b4%e5%9c%a8%e7%bd%91%e4%b8%8a%e5%8f%91%e8%a1%a8%e9%80%80%e5%85%9a%e5%a3%b0/\">自由亚洲｜一名女党员两会期间在网上发表退党声明</a></li>\n<li>12.30<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/12/%e7%bb%b4%e6%9d%83%e7%bd%91-%e5%88%98%e8%90%8d%e5%a5%b3%e5%84%bf%e5%bb%96%e6%95%8f%e6%9c%88%e5%90%91%e8%87%aa%e5%b7%b1%e6%89%80%e5%9c%a8%e5%ad%a6%e6%a0%a1%e9%80%92%e4%ba%a4%e9%80%80%e5%85%9a/\">维权网 | 刘萍女儿廖敏月向自己所在学校递交退党声明</a></li>\n<li>04.05<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/%e7%be%8e%e5%9b%bd%e4%b9%8b%e9%9f%b3-%e5%85%9a%e5%91%98%e9%80%80%e5%85%9a-%e5%85%b1%e4%ba%a7%e4%b8%bb%e4%b9%89%e5%9c%a8%e4%bf%84%e7%bd%97%e6%96%af%e6%97%a0%e5%89%8d%e9%80%94/\">美国之音 | 党员退党 共产主义在俄罗斯无前途</a></li>\n<li>11.24<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/11/%e9%a2%9c%e6%98%8c%e6%b5%b7%e6%b2%a1%e6%9c%89%e4%ba%86%e7%89%b9%e6%9d%83%ef%bc%8c%e5%a4%a7%e6%89%b9%e5%85%9a%e5%91%98%e5%b0%b1%e8%a6%81%e6%b1%82%e9%80%80%e5%85%9a/\">颜昌海:没有了特权，大批党员就要求退党</a></li>\n<li>12.20<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/12/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e6%b0%91%e4%b8%bb%e5%85%9a%e8%bf%9130%e5%90%8d%e5%b0%91%e5%a3%ae%e6%b4%be%e6%88%90%e5%91%98%e9%80%80%e5%85%9a/\">香港民主党近30名少壮派成员退党</a></li>\n<li>09.29<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/%e8%8e%ab%e6%96%af%e7%a7%91%e5%b8%82%e9%95%bf%e5%8d%a2%e6%97%a5%e7%a7%91%e5%a4%ab%e8%a2%ab%e5%85%8d%e8%81%8c%e5%90%8e%e5%ae%a3%e5%b8%83%e9%80%80%e5%85%9a/\">莫斯科市长卢日科夫被免职后宣布退党</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"mceTemp\"></div>\n","author":1052,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[32050,16775,24405]}